                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.60/20: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Barcelona</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Perkins</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Barcelona</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-12-02T18:00:00+00:00"
                            >December 2, 1936—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received December 2—5:15 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My despatches Nos. 88 of October 31, 93 of November 5, and 121 of November
                        21.<note n="7" xml:id="d831fn7">None printed.</note> Catalan Council of
                    Economy has announced that detailed regulations will shortly appear for the
                    collectivization of businesses containing foreign interests and that meanwhile
                    all activities looking to the collectivization of such businesses should be
                    suspended.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Perkins</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
